f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#23嗰位巴打講嘅方法可以做到，sub<br />\n<p class=\"center\"> x=(k^2/&Delta;)/(1+k^2/&Delta;) </p><br />\n然後狂做就執到&beta; function嗰個樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#22嗰位巴打嘅substitution就咁睇個integration boundary會flip左，應該都得但係我未試過。<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}